cloud computing
elastic compute cloud (EC2)
simple storage service (S3)
relational database service (RDS)
virtual private cloud (VPC)
elastic load balancing (ELB)
identity and access management (IAM)
amazon machine image (AMI)
route 53
elasticsearch service

### Note that some of these terms are actually abbreviations (e.g., EC2, S3, RDS, VPC, ELB, IAM, AMI) but I have included them as they are commonly used to refer to specific services within Amazon Web Services.
